polyesterData

polyesterData is a package that loads a simulated OMOP CDM dataset of approximately 6039 patients originally sourced from Synthetic Health’s Synthea using the polyester2 R package. The csvs can also be direcly accessed in the data-raw subdirectory for non-R users.

Installation

You can install the latest version of polyesterData with:

devtools("meerapatelmd/polyesterData")

Load Data

Loading the Drug Exposure Table as an example:

library(polyesterData)  
head(DRUG_EXPOSURE)
